Class DescribeDBParameterGroupsRequest

    ReadLimitInfo, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class DescribeDBParameterGroupsRequest
extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Container for the parameters to the DescribeDBParameterGroups operation.

    Returns a list of DBParameterGroup descriptions. If a DBParameterGroupName is specified, the list will contain only the description of the specified DB parameter group.

    See Also:
    AmazonRDS.describeDBParameterGroups(DescribeDBParameterGroupsRequest), Serialized Form
